query: SELECT p.id, c.name as country, s.name as service, p.smshubPrice, p.ourPrice, p.apiId FROM prices p JOIN countries c ON p.countryId = c.id JOIN services s ON p.serviceId = s.id WHERE p.apiId = 3 LIMIT 10
